            <description><![CDATA[【今日，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A4%A7%E9%9B%AA%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A4%A7%E9%9B%AA%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#大雪#</span></a>❄️ 大家感受到一丝凉意了吗<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】①今日17时33分，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A4%A7%E9%9B%AA%E8%8A%82%E6%B0%94%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#大雪节气#</span></a>到，仲冬时节正式开始。②此时节天气更加寒冷，降雪的可能性也更大。③“小雪腌菜，大雪腌肉”，很多家庭开始腌制“咸货”。④注意防寒保暖，多锻炼，常通风，可适当进补。大雪已至，新年也不远了<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[偷笑]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_touxiao-0d995330b6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkl1epoypgj20u01t2tqk.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkl1eph0usj20u01t2qg8.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkl1eptql8j20u01t1av8.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkl1epr76mj20u01t0tqj.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkl1epv2p8j20u01t2qlm.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkl1eqcg8wj20u01t2tzl.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkl1epuesxj20u01t2nal.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkl1eq6k1pj20u01t1tzu.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkl1eptaolj20u01t1k1u.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
