            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%E5%BF%AB%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E5%80%99%E4%BC%A0%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%BA%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%E5%BF%AB%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E5%80%99%E4%BC%A0%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%BA%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#感冒快好的时候传染性最强吗#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】医生表示，感冒后出现恶寒、发热、头痛的时候是传染性最强的时候。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%E5%88%9A%E5%A5%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%B3%E6%B4%97%E6%BE%A1%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E6%84%9F%E5%86%92%E5%88%9A%E5%A5%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%B3%E6%B4%97%E6%BE%A1%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#医生提醒感冒刚好不要立即洗澡#</span></a> 因为洗澡有可能再次受凉，会出现病情反复和加重，家长照顾孩子的时候最好戴口罩，家里的餐具和工具也要分隔使用<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6l2q2lC" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
